43
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:41,760
I like you.

44
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:42,830
I love you.

45
00:03:43,355 --> 00:03:44,480
I hope you'll love me too.

46
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:46,390
