75
00:05:11,700 --> 00:05:17,060
♪Maybe we were never meant to be♪

76
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:47,620
♪When everything before my eyes♪

77
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:50,350
(I, Gu Liusu,)

78
00:05:50,590 --> 00:05:52,520
(call myself the daughter of the rain.)

79
00:05:54,790 --> 00:05:56,390
