88
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:24,560
I can see everything clearly.

89
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,680
But only me, all alone.

90
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:36,300
♪I'm feeling you from up on a hill♪

91
00:06:39,350 --> 00:06:40,520
You have me now.

92
00:06:44,400 --> 00:06:51,200
